name: I Flew WestJet's INAUGURAL Flight to Seoul!
description:
On May 17th, 2024, WestJet inaugurated flights between Calgary, Canada, and Seoul, South Korea! This is the airline's second ever route to Asia, operating 3x weekly on their flagship Boeing 787-9 Dreamliners.

Predictably, yes, I booked the flight and got to fly on what is now WestJet's longest flight in their network!
